The files contained in this directory are sample files that
were used to create the AmigaGuide version of the Autodocs
for the V1.0 CATS CD.

The autodocs.excepts file must be joined to the autodocs.xref
file.  The autodocs.excepts file contains function names that
are also common words and therefore shouldn't be made into
links.

An assign of TEXT_INCLUDE: must be made to a directory that
contains the unarchived contents of inc37_3.lzh.

The Autodocs file is the file that was used as the table
of contents for the Autodocs on the V1.0 CATS CD.  The icon
is a miniature of the Includes & Autodocs RKM cover.

